	TODO

Add required submodules (Modules from Puppet Labs)
	git submodule add git@github.com:puppetlabs/puppetlabs-apache.git modules/apache
	git submodule add git@github.com:puppetlabs/puppetlabs-stdlib.git modules/stdlib
	git submodule add git@github.com:puppetlabs/puppetlabs-firewall.git modules/firewall
	git submodule add git@github.com:puppetlabs/puppetlabs-mysql.git modules/mysql
	git submodule add git@github.com:nodesagency/puppet-php.git modules/php

Make your manifest file:

	node 'server.example.com' {
		class { 'opencart':
		
		}
	}
